oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Various demo performances - Cedarwood Publishing Company - 1978-12-12
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various demo performances, featuring Dewayne Orender (songwriter/performer), Rusty Summerville (songwriter), Mike Kelly (songwriter), Dewayne Wheaton (songwriter), Eric Daniel (performer), Woody Bomar (songwriter/performer), Michael Heeney (songwriter/performer), Susan Heeney (performer), Paul Trey, and Pat Higdon. Recorded on December 12, 1978 at Cedarwood Studios (Nashville, Tenn.)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (00:00) I Feel Temptation (Dewayne Orender, Rusty Summerville) -- (03:25) Morning Side Of Midnight (Dewayne Orender, Rusty Summerville) -- (06:24) The Last Goodbye (Dewayne Orender, Mike Kelly) -- (09:32) It's Gonna Take Time (Dewyane Orender, Rusty Summerville) -- (12:24) It Was Love (Dewayne Orender, Rusty Summerville, Dewayne Wheaton, [Unidentified]) -- (16:25) All That I Have Ever Wanted (Dewayne Orender, Eric Daniel) -- (18:59) The Jogger (Woody Bomar) -- (22:38) There Ain't No Good In Goodbyes (Susan Heeney) -- (26:31) There Ain't No Good In Goodbyes (Michael Heeney) -- (30:03) Lyin' Here Lyin' (Michael Heeney, Susan Heeney)
